Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:02:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see it, \NTodo is in agony now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been two weeks \Nsince Coach Munakata passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.34,0:02:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the entire tour team, \NTodo is the only one aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo tries his best to not cave in \Nunder the huge pressure of this news, fighting ferociously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But in tournament, he lacks his usual grandeur, \Nstruggling hard even against trifling opponents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In 1st and 2nd rounds, \Nhe managed to win somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But in his current state of mind, \Neven getting into the Best 8 would take a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Katsura{didn't get that "imasakanagara" part}, the decisive measures you took \Nupon Coach Munakata's death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,are subject to my deep admiration these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,By postponing the announcement \Nof Coach Munakata's death until the end of this tour,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you helped to conceal it from everyone, \Nand from Oka in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, by entrusting Oka to a famous Australian coach, Mr. Reynolds, you allowed us to fulfill this tour's purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Have no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, Oka, along with Madame Butterfly and Ozaki, \Nstill has no idea about this death{/ news}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozaki took{guess} the 3rd round effortlessly, \Nwith his natural doggedness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Butterfly secured herself the place \Nin A-block's Best 8 among other foreign players.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Her power is dazzling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,As for Oka, Mr. Reynolds keeps her shaped up by packing her between-matches time tightly with intensive training.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She advanced all the way \Nto B-block quarterfinals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFEFDFF&\bord11\blur11\3c&HFFF9E8&\t(0,1100,\bord0\blur0.4\c&HF2E7E9&\3c&HF1AF5E&)\fnGabriola\fs78\pos(320,390)}Episode 4 \N\N\N\N\NNew York Melancholy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I should be doing this by myself.{one big guess, not sure about a single word here; I came to "私長ないかな (I guess I'm not tall enough.) / 私ならないかな"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach's style is approximately that of a foreigner, \Nso the size should match, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Not quite that. \NWrong, all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What souvenir should I get for Coach? \NNothing is strikingly good here.{/ I just want to pick something decisively good.; slightly unsure about "basshitto" part}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You never managed to decide \Non a souvenir for Coach, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But... How do you know \NI was looking for a souvenir for Coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, when you're free, \Ncome to my room, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Angie Reynolds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Matchups for quarter-finals \Nhave been announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So I came here to inform you personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one you'll be playing against.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Although dad is delirious about coaching you for now, \Nonce I defeat you, dad will certainly come to his senses{/ return to me}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, whatever it takes, \NI am going to defeat you, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to come to your match with Angie \Nthoroughly prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only Coach Reynolds has always been \NAngie's coach only, he is also her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet Mr. Reynolds favored you over his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine Coach Munakata \Nfavoring someone else over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, you get to play a match against that person,\NOka, how do you think you'd react?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a thing, I... \NCannot even fathom{/ imagine}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In this match, your opponent \Nis nothing like anyone you faced before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,On the TV, our Japan's team roster \Nis the hottest topic it seems!{/ they are going wild over our Japanese team selection!}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us are also receiving \Nsome special attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,With that in mind, \Nwhat in the world happened in today's match?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, to yield one set to such an opponent...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a bit out of shape.{/ Wasn't feeling totally well.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All's well that ends well, I guess,{/ I'm glad you won after all,} \Nbut you really had us nervous{/ in suspence} for a moment there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I did my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't sick somehow, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You think a sick man would do a roadwork like that \Nimmediately after the match?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Coach Munakata's condition was serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If Oka finds out, she'll probably be discouraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, this guy also worries about her, \Nso he's out of tune himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. That must be it. \NI can't think of any other cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach Munakata is no longer with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't tell anyone, not even you, about it. \NYou have to forgive me, Ozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Butterfly...\NShe might have some news about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is learning diligently, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Foreigners are mostly fine players too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Spurred{/ Encouraged} by Oka's vigor{unsure about that "ikkisei" part}, \Nthe entire team is fighting hard to win now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Father? You've been acting strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mind \Nsharing your bad mood it with me, do you?{/ I hope you're not having a bad day.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Reika, I think we've had this kind of talk before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The one directly responsible for Oka Hiromi's birth \Nas a tennis player, Ryuzaki Reika, it is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So I always asked you to be a good mentor for Oka, \Nboth in game and in life{he says just "in life" but I'm already taking huge liberties in this convo to make it consistent}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I remember it well. \NIt helps to uphold my own confidence as well.{with every letter spelled, this convo makes less and less sense}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,While Coach Munakata devotes his life fully to{/ invests his heart and soul into / puts his everything into} Oka,\NI take pride in being a direct cause for her birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Munakata devoted to her the rest of his life, \Nbut to Oka Hiromi's tennis, you effectively were the mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, just now, \Nwhy did you put it this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Devoted the rest of his life?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Reika, I have faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my faith in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Coach's detailed checkup \Njust takes longer than it should...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, just when I called you the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,About such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And Hiromi... \NI can't believe he left Hiromi behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Munakata... Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap... I was so inconsiderate{/ unobservant}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I done!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I done!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo, we're supposed to be friends. \NWhy... Why didn't you tell me a word?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What a dimwit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What a dimwit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo and Madame Butterfly \Nare closer to Oka than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They both will probably end up \Nspiraling into desperation{guess; "udzu" means vortex, but I'm clueless what it means here}, along with Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to... \NI have to stand fast for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Ryuzaki, this is Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to stay strong. \NAfter all, it will hurt her more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand? \NHiromi must not notice a single thing off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Oka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you \Nto teach me knitting wool yarn, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured I should make a hand-knit muffler \Nas a souvenir for Coach Munakata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So I bought this wool yarn in the supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I will show Demon Coach, I am perfectly capable \Nof doing this kind of girly things as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.01,0:09:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd drop his jaw amazed, I imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And... Just basics is enough. \NJust one simple way to knit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:10:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, Oka. Perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This Oka Hiromi is no prowessless lass{either that extremely cringe or I just created a masterpieceXD}, Coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This lesson you'll remember for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I really be doing this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm playing quarter-finals tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Angie Reynolds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My tomorrow's opponent, Coach. \NA mighty contender.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But tonight, Coach, \Nknitting this muffler is my first priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When doing a passing shot, \Ntry to hit behind my back{guess in the "mudetsumori" part}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Apply{guess} more power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Received!{guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nailed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A stunning passing shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just an ordinary ball to her, \Nit hits bullseye of my blind spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a single clue of her true power, \Nshe hits such a ball casually!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Man named Munakata that brought this girl up \Ntreasured her for good reason{unsure, 2 meanings, maybe "he received the most regrettable treatment from fate}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Angie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, you know, \NI'm playing a match this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,An important one, quarterfinals!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you give me the usual \Nbefore-the-match intense training?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I think my backhand receive hitting point \Nbecame too loose lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Angie, at the moment, \NI'm busy coaching Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,With Papa's help, \NI'll fasten it back in place at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the court. \NI'm helping Oka practice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Angie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I will always love my Papa no matter what!{/ My love for Papa is still unwavering!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! \NLet's resume it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to remember well the ball course \Nof our today's rally.{this engrish makes no sense but changing it would be dissonorous}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Those would be Angie's crown ball courses \Nfor today's showdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Those passing shots from earlier may yield you initiative \Nin the match, if you persist in hitting them thoughtfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you confiding Angie's crown ball to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Angie's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And she is my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I love her. She is an apple of my eye \Nthat I don't stop caring about at all times.{/ my most important treasure that I never take my eyes off.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But all this treatment \Nshe only receives as my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, Munakata favored you \Nover his sister Midorikawa Ranko, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, why can't I favor you as well \Nover my daughter Angie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One can choose from a variety of roads\Nto put his life on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But while traveling the chosen road, \Nyou have to make sacrifices to let your soul grow.{Lit: how much your soul will mature? - this sentence generally perplexes me and "sacrifice" is purely my invention in order to tie up this line with the adjacent ones}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It is always the right course of action.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, when the time comes \Nto choose a road companion, {/ to blaze that trail,}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you shouldn't favor anyone \Nmerely on the grounds of being your offspring or sibling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Although putting that into practice \Nis seldom a simple task.{/ This is ordealing to apply to reality.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, you must know it better than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,With boundless love \Nand readiness to traverse the edge of the world,{this sentence is indecently complicated so I took huge risks here at the end of my wits}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a man who chose{/ favored} you as a companion \Nto share both good and bad times{I'm really wondering what 求め合い means but it looks like a counterpart for 分かち合う so I sticked to johnny's version of "good and bad times"},
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Munakata Jin, \Nwho will forever stay by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:15:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, your cause \Nshould be aided with all seriousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you now see why I'm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, coach.{maybe write "Coach" capitalized to mark the beginning of her trust and intimacy with him? before now, I only treated Munakata's "Coach" as his proper name}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.50,Sign,,0,0,0,,Munakata Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the old times, today \Nwe exchange hits until we drop dead{ again}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and Munakata \Ntalked about many different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There was but a single time this pouty man \Nlivened up when telling me about this one girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's actually a secret,\Nbut turns out I've got quite a lovely little sister."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That man, who looked like sulkiness was his trademark, \Nsuddenly became so gleeful while talking about her:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"For now, we can't play together yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:17:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But one day, when I start doing tennis just for fun, \NI want to team up with my sister and play in pairs."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As only child in family, \NI was a wee bit jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This... He wanted this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The best of three set match.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Reynolds' service. Play!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa taught Reynolds family tennis to me personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way it loses to a player \Nwho plays tennis for less than 3 years of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,15-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it takes, \Nwith this, I'll make Papa return!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Angie, I like that determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,By clashing with the right opponent, \Nyou were able to find this determination in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Angie moves even better than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,30-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is authentic{/indigenous} power tennis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka, are you not one bit jealous \Nof Todo's or Ozaki's male tennis?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.96,0:19:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of that Todo's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Get this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.11,0:19:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What I taught her just this morning, \NHiromi have mastered already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What a child, Christ's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka's moves became much sharper suddenly. \NShe regained her composure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This shouldn't be possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Advantage: Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka, aim for the ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Game set. \NMatch won by... Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Won...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach Munakata...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,With every Oka's victory, \Nthe return day draws closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think of Oka finding out the truth, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo, I'm going to practice. \NYou coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't lose your own match. \NIf befalls on us now to stand strong for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozaki, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I will also join them for practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Everyone knows at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is trying earnestly \Nto act the most open{/ candid} way about it.{I'm honestly unsure about true meaning of this whole sentence みんな懸命に誠意を尽くして動こうとしている}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.74,0:21:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Munakata, you must be the happiest man ever \Nto have such wonderful students.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, I have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't forget, next time Papa coaches me again, \Nhe'll warn me about your weak points as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have faith in it. \NPapa will definitely return to me in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice play, Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Angie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, I defeated Angie Reynolds today, \Nthe prominent contender!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd make it this far - \Ninto semifinals!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, it's a shame you're missing all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I return home with it, \Nyou'll receive the most detailed record.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'll wrap this muffler around your neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My knitting{/ execution} may be imperfect, \Nbut it's full of{/ sodden with} boundless love!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand, Munakata Jin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheeeeers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.69,0:23:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Aikawa Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.19,0:23:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, Hiromi is coming back at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.86,0:23:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And with a silver medal from finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.00,0:23:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure is in for a big shock, \Nto find out Coach Munakata is no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.60,0:23:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared. The moment Hiromi finds out \Nwill be dreadful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And who in the world is going to deliver to Hiromi \Nthe news of such magnitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.23,0:23:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.23,0:24:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Diary Left Behind
